{"tid":24510,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"仲有20日 女神就係聖誕節當日同第二個瘋狂啪啪啪了","createTime":"2016-12-05T14:39:02.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-05T15:00:19.000Z","uid":7374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"01ff5077d686235cfb3f856d3a064367dc9b97b8","tid":24510,"uid":7374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T14:39:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1818625114c14a48589e46a7b11ead461c2d103","tid":24510,"uid":34323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T14:39:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2668572cadbc04870541991612211cae3fe7a368","tid":24510,"uid":9668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T14:40:31.000Z","msg":"正常啦"},{"pid":"f0e3b970d40571e97825e3df569ceb0bdd407c03","tid":24510,"uid":7374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T14:40:49.000Z","msg":"各位手足請振作面對現實<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2ddd685b39f1161d4c23260aebe38501883b497","tid":24510,"uid":20890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T14:42:28.000Z","msg":"唔好咁諗<br />\n可能依家已經瘋狂啪啪啪"},{"pid":"8d54628bab17d95048a3ec0ea598f3e63700524d","tid":24510,"uid":6981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T14:43:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好咁諗<br />\n可能依家已經瘋狂啪啪啪</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4355e7eca77ba3fbaa70fd6212c6b44c76a85b02","tid":24510,"uid":35105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T14:43:33.000Z","msg":"有時真係唔明啲女人咁撚賤...<br />\n明明已經一齊咁耐，一啲少少新鮮感就另你塊雞西野外露出，之後為左掩飾自己係一個好女仔就用埋啲垃圾藉口講分手，<br />\n<br />\n乜撚野我覺得我地唔同左。<br />\n岩嘅人，錯啲時間。<br />\n我唔適合你嫁啦。<br />\n你屋企人唔中意我<br />\n淡左<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">其實我仲中意你，不過我地冇左啲野</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">冇左乜野？</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">唔知。</span><br />\n屌你個老母，見撚到都燥<br />\n<br />\n仲有大撚把都係離撚晒普，<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講真呀，出邊係花花世界邊個唔知，你覺得自己未玩夠嘅，唔好走出黎累人啦！人地都係想搵個歸宿姐<br />\n<br />\n做男仔嘅都醒下啦<br />\n冇人迫你負出心機時間，<br />\n唔好講到負出心機一定有回報，<br />\n感情嘅野冇左就冇左，<br />\n唔好用藉口去美化自己同人地<br />\n旁觀者清，會睇得出，<br />\n係朋友就快啲屌醒佢。<br />\n但當局者迷，死無對證，係最撚慘，<br />\n多聽身邊朋友嘅睇法，有時客觀咁睇傷得有咁深...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n負出幾多，其實都係自我感覺良好<br />\n唔好諗住你做得多塊西就番轉頭<br />\n人地懶係做撚左籠中鳥，有得自由仲番轉頭咩"},{"pid":"9f2193d9b0f2915556420a04046b331f5c7f5249","tid":24510,"uid":9668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T14:43:41.000Z","msg":"佢之次扑完都send返條片比我"},{"pid":"a77c05c393a63c32328158f55f22bca51f1c36d2","tid":24510,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T14:43:47.000Z","msg":"你都幾樂觀"},{"pid":"8f1c4986b5467e4621e22cdc4d30eb54e8d44ca0","tid":24510,"uid":4622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T14:43:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/05/224340_83c114a5efecdede9859fe34414df8c5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F05%2F224340_83c114a5efecdede9859fe34414df8c5.jpg&h=c12d328f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n防毒軟件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e25a356128aa901